        public abstract boolean downloads(java.io.File file,
                                  java.lang.String remote)
                           throws java.io.IOException,
                                  java.lang.ClassNotFoundException
        Download all files under the file to server if remote is working directory. Download itself if file.isFile() is uri.

        remote - server working directory or uri.
